name: Sealed Projects Container
description:
A sealed container containing unknown objects used by unlisted projects carried out by the Upwell Consortium. Attempts to open it have so far failed, but the secrets it contains will be of special value to some special intelligence operatives.

Can be taken to a Deathless Wraith Trader and exchanged for goods in one of the following systems:
Uttindar
Perimeter
IZ-AOB
Hedion
Hemin
FWST-8
Botane
9IPC-E
UT-UZB
